        h3(class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl mb-2") About

        p(class="text-xl sm:text-2xl") Kilkenny-born Web Developer. Have 19+ years developing with a variety of Web Technologies. BSc. in Computer Science. Currently a Frontend Engineer with InscribeAI.


