        | &middot; #[strong Javascript]; ES5/6, Angular / AngularJS / VueJS / NodeJS (numerous other libraries)
        | &middot; #[strong HTML5]; WAI-AA Accessibility with ARIA land-marking, testing on NVDA, Jaws, VoiceOver and TalkBack
